Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:02.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(450,0)}My child,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:09.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The story I'm about to tell is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:15.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is the story of a long, long journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:22.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)\i1}a story that will be passed down forever from parent to child, starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:40.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so slow. Walk faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:40.39,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:45.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard of a ramen set?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely starving right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:50.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I want more than to eat a ramen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.41,0:00:54.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,unfortunately, I'm broke. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! It's time for a fun puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:00.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pay me afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:08.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:09.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:12.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:13.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:15.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a filthy doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.48,0:01:16.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:17.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:19.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids are best when they're honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:24.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pay me as much as you want, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're honestly telling you it's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:30.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we pay for something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:31.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:33.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:36.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,300)}It's so hot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-Ramen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.51,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs54\c&HB83D41&\pos(644,96)}Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is this girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:17.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does she want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Money...? I have no money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:44.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gooey Concentrated Peach Nectar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're teasing me, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:12.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This drink is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:23.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, the little kids were playing on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:36.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I sat next to you as you slept, I kept thinking it looked fun, and I wanted to play too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been sleeping there since yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:45.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I poked you to try and wake you up, but you didn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so hungry, I couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:54.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I need it for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Just go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:10.51,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:14.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow! Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.44,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am. It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can play with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been following me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we're going to play on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to race and splash water at each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:41.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and when we're finished, we'll say "See you tomorrow!" and go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:45.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds almost like we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:50.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know each other's names yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Misuzu Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But listen! I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:10.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm hungry, I have to earn some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:17.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I followed her blindly home, lured by the thought of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to eat with someone else, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you usually eat alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:25.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy comes home late, and I don't have a daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish eating, let's play, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:33.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. If it gets late,\NI'll have trouble finding a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't found a place to stay yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll probably end up sleeping outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:44.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen. We just met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have no idea who on earth I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in their right mind would let someone like that stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, your mom wouldn't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:58.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's really lax, so I don't think it'll be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I guess one shouldn't talk of one's parents like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, it's okay for you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:06.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired. I don't have the energy to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can play tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation, so I have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:12.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:23.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think math is useful for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will quadratic functions be useful for me in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why am I helping you with your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your eyes are too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, you sound just like Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:49.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She crashed her motorcycle into the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure it's okay for me to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I'll persuade her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not how you said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! No discussion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can let a young guy like him stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:09.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you to stop saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know Misuzu?
