Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:33.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you seem to have guts. I like that part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:35.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yukito-san is a very good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let him stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Of course! I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:44.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are two conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll sleep in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You will have a drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.36,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:56.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in the end, this is what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Perhaps the one who fell in love was me."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I told him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:09.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The fish you let escape was a mermaid,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That struck home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's at her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, freeloader. Why are you looking so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My eeeeeyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:26.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:31.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything, like a story of an\Nerotic confession of love or a hidden talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:33.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the doll from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This trick is how I earn a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:52.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother also used to travel with this as her profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this have a punch line?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:59.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. You're not funny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it amazing he's not using any tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it had obvious strings showing, it would be better if it were funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:13.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! He's leaving on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter that you don't have any talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just down the sorrow with some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one more glass, missus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:29.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you my name so that you wouldn't call me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:32.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! You're such an insensitive guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a runaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you chasing a goal or a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, compared to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I have a pretty good eye for judging men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let you stay for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:03.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen her reckless side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:11.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's impulsive, and once something catches her eye, she'll be attracted to it like a bee to honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:12.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a babysitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, can you stop her saying that phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gao!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what she says when\Nshe's frustrated or about to cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's supposed to sound like a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:29.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves dinosaurs. She's been saying that since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:32.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to take remedial classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Haruko already left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She leaves early every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:55.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time in a while that I've eaten breakfast with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, what are you going to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll walk you to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:06.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko asked me to watch you so that you don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She still doesn't trust me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a map of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It will show you where you people gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be useful for your work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-chin is in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to pick you up after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
