Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:54.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how she sees the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:06.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you this town's local legendary creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:13.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he really is, I'll do it a favor, then it'll give me something in return, just like in those fairytales.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko... Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it such a great trick that it makes you feel like giving me something in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Piko... Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:30.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:32.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikooo~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko-Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.02,Air Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:38.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pi-P-Pi-Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko. Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:56.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break, you evil extraterrestial creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko... Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:14:59.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:01.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:17.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange extraterrestrial creature stole my doll and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:18.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato isn't an extraterrestrial creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a stray dog from my neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's actually a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko! Piko piko piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry he caused you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:44.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Potato said that he took your doll and ran here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he wanted to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:46.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can understand what he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko, piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are worlds here on Earth I know nothing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:00.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:05.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kano Kirishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:16.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukito Kunisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm naming you Carefree Planet citizen Number 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:26.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Number 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Potato is Number 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:31.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does a Carefree citizen do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fate of a Carefree citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? We have nothing to do, do we, Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll say good-bye for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a Carefree citizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually believed that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:01.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all the girls who wear that uniform weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.09,0:17:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:09.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever wondered what you would do if you had magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:16.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:33.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did your work go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry; I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any business until there are more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:48.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this place so quiet when people should be returning from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this station has been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:53.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gao~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:05.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko told me to scold you when you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He-... Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:34.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes! Quite a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:35.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Basking in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's evening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:48.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi Tohno. She's my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:56.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the top of our class, and is the president of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:01.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just call me Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:12.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito-san is flying like a leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's hurry up and go back to blowing bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:18.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I'm doing really good now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Michiru, Minagi's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:26.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tohno-san's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:33.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of Minagi's classmates too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:38.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an innocent passer-by who just got bowled over by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi, this is a perverted kidnapper who's come to take us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on this side too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a kidnapper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! He's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:53.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Us young girls are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it made a cool sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:05.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a traveler who is staying with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:10.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hope left if you're a\Nperverted homeless kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san, I think we'd best be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I was finally able to make nice bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-Kami too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-Kami... Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting dark, so let's do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pack a lunch for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiya~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:49.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:51.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you should get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:01.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, for tomorrow's lunch,\Ncan you make hamburgers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong to that brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:15.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't made a single yen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were standing there like that when we met yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:24.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was little, I've had this longing for the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:25.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:28.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:33.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this feeling that my other self is out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a romantic thought, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That the real me is in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:41.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to see far into the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:47.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everything on earth would seem so insignificant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:51.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and one would find a kind feeling towards others, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:08.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me, that was the start of a summer as short as a star's twinkle, and as long as eternity.{\fad(0,600)\i0}
