Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:45.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be the other you that I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:47.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out to be a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:50.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have stayed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:53.12,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:54.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:55.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:58.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:00.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a world I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:03.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything extends endlessly into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:05.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:08.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,did you have wings in your dream?
