Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.30,0:02:03.45,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}We watched the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.90,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}They were so dazzling, I ran away
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.91,0:02:17.28,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}I was so frustrated, I released your hand
