Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.89,0:02:32.21,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}She gazes at  it, keeping her wish to herself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.52,0:02:40.66,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Children walk along the summer railway tracks
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.89,0:02:47.22,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Holding in both hands their wishes to take flight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.42,0:02:54.51,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Chasing, chasing the fading vapor trails
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.38,0:03:02.16,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}It hasn't changed since the day we crossed that hill
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.16,0:03:04.42,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And never will
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.49,0:03:10.56,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}And just as we are now, standing tall
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.06,0:03:19.47,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}We'll guard the strength of a sea god
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.65,0:03:24.57,AirOPEng,,0000,0000,0000,karaoke,{\fad(250,250)}Surely
